        public SwerveModule(SpeedController _spinController,

        Swerve Module basic constructor
        Parameters:
        _spinController - SpeedController of the spin motor
        _driveController - SpeedController of the drive motor
        _spinEncoder - Encoder to tell the angle of the drive wheel (may be changed to a Potentiometer)
        _driveEncoder - Encoder to tell the position of the drive wheel (may be changed to a Potentiometer)

      • SwerveModule

        public SwerveModule(String _name,
                    SpeedController _driveController,
                    SpeedController _spinController,
                    Encoder _spinEncoder,
                    Encoder _driveEncoder,
                    double _Pk,
                    double _Ik,
                    double _Dk)
        Advanced Swerve Module constructor with adjustable PID values
        Parameters:
        _name - the name of the module
        _spinController - SpeedController of the spin motor
        _driveController - SpeedController of the drive motor
        _spinEncoder - Encoder to tell the angle of the drive wheel (may be changed to a Potentiometer)
        _driveEncoder - Encoder to tell the position of the drive wheel (may be changed to a Potentiometer)
        _Pk - P constant for PID for both loops
        _Ik - I constant for PID for both loops
        _Dk - D constant for PID for both loops
